1
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:11,880
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Yes, my father did
work in that godforsaken house.</font></b>

2
00:00:13,599 --> 00:00:16,079
<b><font color='#fed64e'>He was head of
the hospital back then.</font></b>

3
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:20,359
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I was very little,
