5
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:34,200
<b><font color='#fed64e'>It was about half a year ago.</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>She came to visit.</font></b>

6
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:38,479
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I could tell right away
