7
00:00:39,679 --> 00:00:42,320
<b><font color='#fed64e'>It didn't take much prodding.</font></b>

8
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:47,880
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Apparently she
owed money, a lot of it,</font></b>

9
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:52,200
<b><font color='#fed64e'>to some very</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'> scary people.</font></b>

10
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:55,920
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I told her not to worry.</font></b>

11
00:00:56,399 --> 00:01:01,520
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Move out here," I said. "Start
