12
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:05,000
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I mean, what am I
going to do with all this?"</font></b>

13
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:09,719
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But she wouldn't have it.</font></b>

14
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:13,079
<b><font color='#fed64e'>She was a good girl at heart.</font></b>

15
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:18,480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Hated seeing me sell my
inheritance to pay her debts.</font></b>

16
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But I could
tell it was serious.</font></b>

17
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:31,319
<b><font color='#fed64e'>And so I lost my
good sense, fool that I am.</font></b>

18
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:37,120
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"There may be
another way," I said.</font></b>

19
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:43,159
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"I held my tongue for decades,</font></b>

