00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:49,239
<b><font color='#fed64e'>but it was so hard</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>to see her suffer so</font></b>

21
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,359
<b><font color='#fed64e'>much good </font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>did that to her."</font></b>

22
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:59,159
<b><font color='#fed64e'>My father was a
very successful man,</font></b>

23
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:02,200
<b><font color='#fed64e'>as was his father before him.</font></b>

24
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:06,480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>As the war drew nearer,</font></b>

25
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:09,639
<b><font color='#fed64e'>my parents only realized </font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>they would have to flee</font></b>

26
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:13,039
<b><font color='#fed64e'>when it was almost too late.</font></b>

27
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:18,240
<b><font color='#fed64e'>It certainly wasn't possible </font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>to get out any amount of wealth.</font></b>

28
