31
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,560
<b><font color='#fed64e'>He bought up lots of gold.</font></b>

32
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:39,400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>People were
hiding their treasures</font></b>

33
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:42,240
<b><font color='#fed64e'>in the walls and
the cellars of their houses.</font></b>

34
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:45,479
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But my father
saw that wasn't safe,</font></b>

35
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,639
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and he came up with a plan.</font></b>

36
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:54,599
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Hide it at the
hospital, in the Faust House."</font></b>

37
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,120
<b><font color='#fed64e'>So we fled,</font></b>

38
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:03,840
<b><font color='#fed64e'>first to London and
eventually to the States.</font></b>

39
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:07,560
<b><font color='#fed64e'>My father got a job
at a hospital in Connecticut,</font></b>

40
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:12,759
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and he never did get a
