41
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:17,039
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Towards the end
he was a man possessed.</font></b>

42
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:22,439
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"That's your wealth
hidden in that house," he said.</font></b>

43
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,120
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Your future hidden
in that house," he said.</font></b>

44
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:29,919
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Your future,
always the future."</font></b>

45
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:31,879
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Ambition.</font></b>

46
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:38,479
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I seem to be the only one
