50
00:03:57,360 --> 00:04:02,479
<b><font color='#fed64e'>After I told
Sara, she was changed.</font></b>

51
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,479
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Soon after,</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>moved out here</font></b>

52
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:09,240
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and got a job</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'> in that house.</font></b>

53
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I comforted myself.</font></b>

54
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:20,040
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Thinking whatever</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'> had been hidden there</font></b>

55
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,800
<b><font color='#fed64e'>would surely</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>long be gone.</font></b>

56
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:25,600
<b><font color='#fed64e'>She wouldn't find anything</font></b>

57
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:31,079
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and eventually come to
her senses and accept my offer.</font></b>

58
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:34,399
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But now I think...</font></b>